G careers' Weekend Helps Define Black-While conflict
Where the
Truth parts
_ By Tom THOMAS
The most obvious simulation between
the‘recent Black carter's program and
last years’ discussions [allowing the
investigation of Dr. King was the recipient question: “What is the role of
the white individual who is concerned,
impathic, active, etc?” It is perhaps
significant of the transition of the “civil
right movement” to a Black generation
struggle met this year the questions
seemed to be but watches and the answers
seemed far more difficult to find.
To understand the complexity of this
